metadata.name: GOTHAM
metadata.description: Capturing the magic in Gotham , how beautiful the snow rolled in and made a great composition in the foreground, The reason why I called this piece Gotham because of me creating a new style of photography I started getting into cinematic way of editing and creating a different look, Now who ever buys this piece get a physical print on acrylic glass and a thank you letter and a 15% of your next purchase also you have to let me know so I can send the offer to you , for being there for me in my creative process of finding Saad , thank you from the bottom of my heart.
